  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Shifting the Power through developing the capacity of local NGOs</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">General Objectives 
The general objective of this project is to enable HUNDEE has emergency preparedness plan in place and deliver effective and efficient humanitarian response.
Specific Objectives 
The specific objectives of the project include:
&#x2022;	To enhance management capacity and technical skills of fifteen staff members of the organization in the project period so that they deliver humanitarian response; 
&#x2022;	To institutionalize humanitarian response procedures in the organization&#x2019;s systems of operation in the project period; and
&#x2022;	To enhance HUNDEE&#x2019;s participation in emergency related meetings done at different levels and influence decisions.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The specific project activities are: I) Build emergency management and coordination capacity of staff to deliver humanitarian response through establishing humanitarian taskforce; Provide emergency management and leadership capacity building training; arrange experience sharing visit; avail and familiarize international humanitarian standard; assign responsible personnel and provide capacity building training. II) Institutionalize humanitarian response procedures in the organization through Review and update of organizational policies; develop comprehensive organizational emergency preparedness plan; conduct consultative and validation meeting/workshop with staff members and other concerned bodies and Prepare checklists and guidelines for emergency assessment</narrative>
  </description>
